_:Neb27d3b2dc9641aeb48d0b5ec8ad3045 <http://schema.org/description> "<p>Professor Bethany Shinkins is a Professor of Health Economics at Warwick Medical School at the University of Warwick.</p>\n\n<p>Bethany has a longstanding interest in screening and is a test expert member of the UK National Screening Committee. She is a co-investigator on the Yorkshire Lung Screening Trial, a randomised controlled trial to evaluate community-based low-dose CT screening for lung cancer, and iDx-LUNG which is a biomarker study embedded within the Lung Health Check.</p>\n" .
